INSERT INTO affected_entities (
                alert_id,
                route_id,
                bus_route_id,
                stop_id,
                sort_order
            )
            SELECT
                unnest($1::uuid[]),
                unnest($2::text[]),
                unnest($3::text[]),
                unnest($4::text[]),
                unnest($5::int[])
            ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
